9f63574c-bec7-4a8c-be02-7983e9268882.title: Old crone
9f63574c-bec7-4a8c-be02-7983e9268882.text:
When 100 years old you reach, look like a prune you
will.

4cfd34a3-c6dc-464e-940b-52c465bce5fb.title: Old crone
4cfd34a3-c6dc-464e-940b-52c465bce5fb.text: I lived here when this was all just fields, you know.

b5e47ece-b753-4c1c-90ad-e2dff4b6c898.title: <player>
b5e47ece-b753-4c1c-90ad-e2dff4b6c898.text: I'm here about the farmers east of here.

edf5bb1f-d447-4f7b-9784-5df14edf8227.title: <player>
edf5bb1f-d447-4f7b-9784-5df14edf8227.text:
Alice and her husband are having trouble talking to one
another and said you might be able to help.

480e668e-1c8b-435e-a761-8d74eb6ec23e.title: Old crone
480e668e-1c8b-435e-a761-8d74eb6ec23e.text:
Ah, I know them; shame about those cows. Why would
they think that I could help?

285701e9-ac18-4e9e-98a0-ce6a30983410.title: <player>
285701e9-ac18-4e9e-98a0-ce6a30983410.text:
Alice seems to think you could alter a ghostspeak amulet
in order to allow them to communicate.

1fe7d03f-af84-441f-9ea5-a86ee9c80203.title: Old crone
1fe7d03f-af84-441f-9ea5-a86ee9c80203.text:
Well, the poor young lady has such family problems; I
quite feel her pain. I'd be happy to help.

1581ba9e-6cd9-420a-9215-1984117aac87.title: Old crone
1581ba9e-6cd9-420a-9215-1984117aac87.text:
You seem to have one of her golden hairs on your
shoulder, so I can use that...

ed668b5d-7a62-4aaa-88b8-25df00b99909.title: Old crone
ed668b5d-7a62-4aaa-88b8-25df00b99909.text:
Talk to me again with a ghostspeak amulet and some
space in your backpack and I'll be ready to work on
this little good deed. The way I plan is quite simple,
really.

5c711d32-7ed7-48aa-ac4d-f9b5ce5e92c5.title: Old crone
5c711d32-7ed7-48aa-ac4d-f9b5ce5e92c5.text:
I can mirror part of the unused mystical essence of the
ghostspeak amulet, bind it with Alice's hair and thus
create a second amulet.

8f4d674e-44c3-4cb3-9913-0750e70c0176.title: Old crone
8f4d674e-44c3-4cb3-9913-0750e70c0176.text:
The second amulet will be useful for the purpose you
desire, though it won't work for any other ghost or
human other than the farmer and his wife.

5d1e67c8-3329-41c5-b1ea-75b7d34a65ef.title: <player>
5d1e67c8-3329-41c5-b1ea-75b7d34a65ef.text: I'm here about the farmers east of here.

edc05809-de16-44e2-9bb9-64a2e0a01787.title: <player>
edc05809-de16-44e2-9bb9-64a2e0a01787.text:
I'm here to see if you are ready to do your mystical
stuff with my ghostspeak amulet.

18e9bf55-5623-442a-a3b9-e3a221238182.title: Old crone
18e9bf55-5623-442a-a3b9-e3a221238182.text:
I most certainly am, but you don't have space in your
backpack.

97bdd456-d80f-4136-9288-7be742a6b733.title: Old crone
97bdd456-d80f-4136-9288-7be742a6b733.text: I most certainly am; there you go.

020315a7-bfe5-42ee-959c-ade4b26103f8.title: <player>
020315a7-bfe5-42ee-959c-ade4b26103f8.text: Wow, that was quick and painless.

0b606d45-5ac0-4863-bee8-25f46ac1eec6.title: <player>
0b606d45-5ac0-4863-bee8-25f46ac1eec6.text: I'm here about the farmers east of here.

28385a21-1289-4a53-9c90-aa68fe9e9500.title: <player>
28385a21-1289-4a53-9c90-aa68fe9e9500.text:
I'm here to see if you are ready to do your mystical
stuff with my ghostspeak amulet.

93c64770-74a9-43fe-bec4-67587a8826e8.title: Old crone
93c64770-74a9-43fe-bec4-67587a8826e8.text:
I most certainly am, but you don't have space in your
backpack.

729a76bf-6304-4b19-a959-46877b967a9f.title: <player>
729a76bf-6304-4b19-a959-46877b967a9f.text:
Well, to tell the truth, I just came back to chat with
you. Any news?

5bfc2418-ec90-4946-a72a-95497e73d233.title: Old crone
5bfc2418-ec90-4946-a72a-95497e73d233.text:
Disgraceful! Deliver the amulet, a young lady's
happiness depends upon it.

636e0790-a3fd-499e-828e-1cdaee264a04.title: <player>
636e0790-a3fd-499e-828e-1cdaee264a04.text:
Would you be able to replace the amulet you made? I
seem to have lost it.

85c7dd51-1ea0-4478-8431-d7c8bd6d0acb.title: Old crone
85c7dd51-1ea0-4478-8431-d7c8bd6d0acb.text:
I most certainly am, but you don't have a ghostspeak
amulet.

47269411-3cff-44bf-98a4-d48efe9d34ef.title: Old crone
47269411-3cff-44bf-98a4-d48efe9d34ef.text:
Here you are; luckily, I saved some of Alice's hair in
case you were careless. Which you were.

6ce23499-7216-46df-b274-4ebc6dacc7b1.title: <player>
6ce23499-7216-46df-b274-4ebc6dacc7b1.text: I'm here about the farmers east of here.

7f142f4f-adc2-4ca8-8118-e225a267a036.title: <player>
7f142f4f-adc2-4ca8-8118-e225a267a036.text:
Hello there, just dropping in to thank you again. It all
went perfectly. Alice and her husband can communicate
again.

8697e1bf-c439-4360-bf69-f4d6092a0365.title: Old crone
8697e1bf-c439-4360-bf69-f4d6092a0365.text:
I can't help but shed a tear about my own family. My
sisters are so vile, I refuse to talk to them these days.

5e4975b6-9500-4b2e-bc09-9a0621733711.title: Old crone
5e4975b6-9500-4b2e-bc09-9a0621733711.text:
Never mind; we've reunited a happy family of farmers;
that's enough for me.
